Members.Name: contactPhoneNumber
Members.Description: Must provide at least one of contactPhoneNumber, homePhoneNumber, or mobilePhoneNumber

Members.Name: homePhoneNumber
Members.Description: Must provide at least one of contactPhoneNumber, homePhoneNumber, or mobilePhoneNumber

Members.Name: mobilePhoneNumber
Members.Description: Must provide at least one of contactPhoneNumber, homePhoneNumber, or mobilePhoneNumber

Members.Name: registrationType
Members.Description:
Valid values are: Mobile and Web.
								Mobile: Returns a key to complete the
								registration. Web: Returns a URL to
								complete the registration.

Members.Name: showMobileConfirm
Members.Description:
Ask end-user to also initiate confirmation of their mobile phone. 
								This number must be supplied by the API caller (using mobilePhoneNumber)
								Default=false.

Members.Name: useMiniBrowser
Members.Description:
If provided, end user will go through a  
								single page sign-up flow on a Mini Browser.
								If not provided, flow defaults to the 
								Multi-page flow that is full size.

Members.Name: performExtraVettingOnThisAccount
Members.Description:
Set to true if you want this account to undergo extra vetting by PayPal
								before becoming usable.

Members.Name: taxId
Members.Description: tax id, ssn, itin, pan, cpf, acn, abn, etc.

Members.Name: businessInfo
Members.Description: Required for business account creation

Members.Name: category
Members.Description:
PayPal Business Category. i.e., baby -
								1004

Members.Name: subCategory
Members.Description:
Paypal Business subcategory. i.e.,
								baby-clothing - 2027

Members.Name: merchantCategoryCode
Members.Description:
If Category and Subcategory is
								specified, then this is optional. PayPal
								uses the industry standard Merchant
								Category Codes. Please refer to your
								Association Merchant Category Code
								documentation for a list of codes

Members.Name: companyId
Members.Description: Company Id: tax id, acn, abn, etc.

Members.Name: averagePrice
Members.Description: Average transaction value.

Members.Name: averageMonthlyVolume
Members.Description: Average monthly transaction value.

Members.Name: percentageRevenueFromOnline
Members.Description: Percentage of the revenue that is from online sales (0%-100%).

Members.Name: salesVenueDesc
Members.Description:
Description of store front or place for sales.
								Only required when "OTHER" is specified for
								salesVenue.

Members.Name: vatId

Members.Description: Country code for country on the vat id.

Members.Description: Official commercial registration location.
